'''南方淑女'''（{{lang-en|Southern belle}}）是[[美国深南部|美国深南部]]上层社会年轻女子的[[定型角色|定型角色]]。这一形象源自[[美国|美国]]{{link-en|美国历史 (1779-1849)|History of the United States (1789–1849)|南北战争前}}{{link-en|种植园经济|Plantation economy|种植园主}}上层社会的年轻未婚白人妇女。<ref name="richmond1">{{cite web |url=http://historyengine.richmond.edu/episodes/view/2259 |title=History Engine: Tools for Collaborative Education and Research | Episodes |publisher=Historyengine.richmond.edu |date= |accessdate=September 26, 2013 |archive-date=2020-08-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200807080059/http://historyengine.richmond.edu/episodes/view/2259 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

==形象==
南方淑女的典型形象是身着南北战争前的流行服饰，如{{link-en|铁环长裙|Hoop skirt}}、[[束腹|束腹]]、{{link-en|宽松长裤|Pantalettes}}、宽边草帽和手套。通常会手持阳伞或扇子，在当时晒黑的皮膚是劳动阶级的特徵，南方淑女會避免曬黑。<ref name="richmond1"/> 

南方淑女的理想伴侣是嫁给有声望的年轻男子，并成为专注奉献于家庭和社区的女士。<ref name="richmond1"/> 南方淑女的典型形象具备{{link-en|南部友善|Southern hospitality}}的特色，即保有美丽、贞洁而不失轻佻的品行。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://deepsouthmag.com/2011/06/anatomy-of-a-southern-belle/ |title=Anatomy of a Southern Belle | Deep South Magazine – Southern Food, Travel & Lit |publisher=Deepsouthmag.com |date=June 2, 2011 |accessdate=September 26, 2013 |archive-date=2016-03-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303232711/http://deepsouthmag.com/2011/06/anatomy-of-a-southern-belle/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

